chat.msg: hola, q tal? ready to go?
Hola. Si, Listo para ir
great, so i am at the starting point right now, near the twig
where should i go next?
Muy bien, para tener mayor certeza, que animal te aparece mas cercano a su posicion?
i see a tiger on a small nearby island
should i head that way?
Correcto, tome esa ruta y se dirige hacia la otra isla, atarvesando una rama que esta encima del agua y apenas toque tierra, se detiene para nueva instruccion
alright, i just crossed over to the island with the tiger
what's next, friend?

Aleje el tigre, busque que se quede en la misma posicion. Ahora, frente a usted ve a un pajaro, rodeelo, desde su mano derecha, repito viendolo de frente y cuando ya este de espaldas al pajaro, encontrara unos piedras que atraviesa el agua,
okay, i just walked around the bird from right and now at the stones that cross the water
which way now?
acerquese hasta la rana por el ¿
hey, now i'm near the frog
where to now, mate?
por el lado izquierdo de la rana, vaya hasta el final y devuelvase y atraviese por encima del cocodrilo, luego ve una piedra
were able to navigate past the croc and now near a rock
hola, q tal? ready to play?
Hola. Si, listo.
perfect! first, from where the little white dog is, walk a few steps to your left along a path and cross towards the flower stand
but wait! Don't go straight to him. make a 180 degree change of direction and go back the way you came
Listo, quede nuevamente en el mismo punto de salida
perfect, that's just what I expected. Now, cross the path just over the branch, and continue south
you will find another white dog, but this time next to a red and white checkered picnic tablecloth. You see it?
Ya estoy cerca al perro y al mantel del picnic
bien! now, the next point to note is a bowl of berries
step over the picnic blanket, make sure you touch the berry bowl and then keep moving to your left
Listo
well, very well
follow the path leading to the river, you'll find another wooden branch over there. cross the river over this branch and head north
Ya cruce
perfecto! avoid the green bush ahead of you and circle it from the right side until you reach the flower stand
Ya estoy en el puesto de flores
genial! now turn left and move below the stand until you come across a large bridge with two people on bikes
proceed along that same path past the bridge
Ya atravese el puente
good job! take a few steps south now
readjust your route between the sweet old folks on a bench and another branch
Ya estoy en la rama
good job! now proceed further west
you'll soon find a green bush right next to the end of the wooden branch. see it?
Listo
awesome! just a bit more now
proceed east now, pass between the branch and the bush
hola, q tal? ready to go?
Hola. Si, Listo.
nice! here is our start point at the tent in the north. right now, i see a dog sitting left of a fire, south of us
and a red mushroom to the right of the fire. how should i get going?
Camina hasta pasar frente al perro, luego pasa por el intermedio del perro y el fuego y luego pasa en el medio del fuego y el hongo.
gotcha! so, walked passed the dog to the fire then between the fire and the mushroom
now, i see a blue car to the south and further south there's a blue telescope. what's next, cap?
Acerquese al carro sin tocarlo, hace un giro de 180. luego unos cortos pasos, hasta llegar al camino que lo dirige al telescopio
okay! moved towards the car, spun 180, took a few steps, now on the pathway to the telescope
Parado frente al lente frontal del telescopio, atravieselo en medio del arbusto, tome el sendero y camine unos pasos hasta que vea la casa de enfrente, antes del las piedras que rodean la casa
alright, went through the front of the telescope, passed the bush and followed the path
now, i'm in front of the house with the surrounding rocks. mission accomplished! *finished*
hola, you ready?
Listo
awesome! okay, head southwest under the first palm tree, turn right at the second one, then take a sharp left before the third one
continue south, okay?
Listo
perfect! now, you see that brown puppy? move to its left, turn a bit left and then right towards the south
Listo, quede frente al mar
great, now cross between the big rock on your left and the small rock on your right to reach the water
Ya en el agua
awesome! now face the big red crab, then turn right and keep the big rock on your side as you walk west in the water
Estoy frente al tiburon, que hago?
take a sharp right turn! now, head back to the shore
can you see the medium rock and the blue-yellow-white ball? good, cross between those
Listo
alrighty! Veer slightly to your left and keep heading north
you're doing well! can you see a red tent and a larger speaker? head among those
ya pase en el medio de la carpa y altavoz
perfect! now, circle the tent in an arc and walk south towards the sea
stop just before you hit the water
Llegue al agua
great! now, take a right turn, walk west and go below the red kayak
Ya
fantastic! turn right again, keep the kayak on your side and head north until you reach a small green bush
you've nailed it!
